summary:
FUCK EVERYONE WHO MAKES HUMAN!GORI BLACK and’or DARKSKINNED
EDIT: In response to the “you’re not black. Be quiet you don’t speak...
body:
FUCK EVERYONE WHO MAKES HUMAN!GORI BLACK and’or DARKSKINNED

EDIT: In response to the “you’re not black. Be quiet you don’t speak for us. I’m black and I’m okay with this.”

I’m relaying information I’ve learned and I’m trying to speak on something I feel was a fucked up decision. But honestly it’s a proper argument.

So here is an article written by a Black Woman who makes a compelling argument on why the character of Gori is just plain racist and unacceptable.

It’s sad because she’s one of my favourite characters honestly. But anyway I’m gonna stay in my lane and let you all read the article for yourselves and come to your own conclusions.
